081,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/02\/muhammad-sunlight-shining-face\/","url_meta":{"origin":5441,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Sunlight shining from his face","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: I have not seen anyone more graceful than the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as if the sunlight emanated from his face. I have not seen anyone quicker in his walking than the Prophet, as if the earth was folded for him. We\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11361,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/15\/sahabah-iman-greater-mountains\/","url_meta":{"origin":5441,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Umar on Sahaba: Faith of companions greater than mountains","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah reported: It was asked of Ibm Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cDid the companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, laugh?\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cYes, and the faith in their hearts was greater than the mountains.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf 'Abd al-Razza\u0304q 20976 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":5441,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6555,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/umar-converts-to-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":5441,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Umar: The Prophet prays for Umar&#8217;s conversion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, strengthen Islam with one of two men whom you love more: Abu Jahl or Umar ibn al-Khattab.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cThe most beloved of the two was Umar.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3681 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":5441,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-between-maghrib-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":5441,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Continuous praying between Maghrib and Isha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: I came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I performed the evening prayer with him. The Prophet continued to pray until the evening prayer. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3781 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5441","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5441"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5441\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5441"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5441"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5441"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}